---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="AICP — Roadmap" description="The AICP (Agent Interaction Control Protocol) roadmap. Seven phases from reframing to ecosystem.">

<nav class="mx-auto flex max-w-5xl items-center justify-between px-6 py-6 md:px-12">
  <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-2.5 text-foreground" aria-label="AICP home">
    <svg width="28" height="20" viewBox="0 0 28 20" fill="none" aria-hidden="true">
      <circle cx="9" cy="10" r="7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
      <circle cx="19" cy="10" r="7.5" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"/>
    </svg>
    <span class="text-[22px] font-bold tracking-tight">AICP</span>
  </a>
  <div class="flex items-center gap-5 md:gap-7">
    <a href="/" class="text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground">Home</a>
    <a href="/spec" class="text-sm font-medium text-muted-foreground transition-colors hover:text-foreground">Spec</a>
    <a href="/cosign" class="rounded-md border border-border px-4 py-1.5 text-sm font-semibold text-foreground transition-colors hover:bg-primary hover:text-primary-foreground">Co-Sign</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<section class="mx-auto max-w-[760px] px-6 pt-16 pb-20">
  <span class="font-mono text-[11px] uppercase tracking-[2.5px] text-muted-foreground">Roadmap</span>
  <h1 class="mt-4 text-4xl font-extrabold leading-tight tracking-tight md:text-[48px] md:tracking-[-1.5px]">
    Seven phases to a standard.
  </h1>
  <p class="mt-6 text-[17px] leading-relaxed text-muted-foreground">
    AICP is planned as a protocol suite. The roadmap spans from initial framing through
    binding standardization, profile hardening, conformance, and ecosystem growth.
  </p>

  <div class="mt-12 flex flex-col">
    {[
      { phase: 'A', name: 'Reframing', desc: 'Charter, suite architecture, neutrality posture, enhancement process.', status: 'done' },
      { phase: 'B', name: 'Foundation Draft', desc: 'Hard-normative semantic core, initial object family, schema alignment.', status: 'active' },
      { phase: 'C', name: 'Bindings', desc: 'HTTP first, then JSON-RPC, gRPC, events/webhooks.', status: 'planned' },
      { phase: 'D', name: 'Profiles', desc: 'MCP v1, A2A v1, auth profiles, payment profiles.', status: 'planned' },
      { phase: 'E', name: 'Domain Families', desc: 'Provisioning, commerce, jobs as protocol families.', status: 'planned' },
      { phase: 'F', name: 'Conformance', desc: 'Layered TCK, replay fixtures, two independent implementations.', status: 'planned' },
      { phase: 'G', name: 'Ecosystem', desc: 'Neutral consortium, external governance, cosigner network.', status: 'planned' },
    ].map(({ phase, name, desc, status }) => (
      <div class="flex items-center gap-5 border-b border-border/60 py-5">
        <span class="font-mono text-[12px] text-muted-foreground min-w-[64px]">Phase {phase}</span>
        <div class="flex-1">
          <span class="text-[15px] font-semibold text-foreground">{name}</span>
          <p class="mt-0.5 text-[13px] text-muted-foreground">{desc}</p>
        </div>
        {status === 'done' && (
          <span class="rounded bg-primary px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] text-primary-foreground">DONE</span>
        )}
        {status === 'active' && (
          <span class="rounded border border-border px-3 py-1 font-mono text-[10px] text-muted-foreground">ACTIVE</span>
        )}
      </div>
    ))}
  </div>

  <h2 class="mt-16 text-2xl font-bold tracking-tight">What is working today</h2>
  <div class="mt-8 grid grid-cols-1 gap-8 sm:grid-cols-2">
    <div>
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-foreground border-b border-border pb-2 block">Implemented</span>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3">
        {[
          'Schema-backed spec pack validation',
          'Core protocol types, IDs, version negotiation',
          'Evidence chain creation and verification',
          'Policy evaluation with fail-closed behavior',
          'MCP capability discovery and invocation',
          'Approval gating for high-risk actions',
          'Reference HTTP server with durable state',
        ].map(item => (
          <span class="text-[14px] text-foreground/80">{item}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
    <div>
      <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[1.5px] text-muted-foreground border-b border-border pb-2 block">Coming</span>
      <div class="mt-4 flex flex-col gap-3">
        {[
          'Suite-level binding family',
          'Hard-normative A2A and payment profiles',
          'Domain protocol families',
          'Registry infrastructure',
          'Cross-implementation conformance',
          'External governance structure',
        ].map(item => (
          <span class="text-[14px] text-muted-foreground">{item}</span>
        ))}
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>

  <div class="mt-16 flex flex-wrap gap-3">
    <a href="/cosign" class="rounded-lg bg-primary px-7 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-primary-foreground transition-opacity hover:opacity-85">Become a Co-Signer</a>
    <a href="https://github.com/EfeDurmaz16/OAPS/blob/main/ROADMAP.md" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="rounded-lg border border-border px-7 py-3 text-sm font-semibold text-foreground transition-colors hover:border-muted-foreground">Full Roadmap on GitHub</a>
  </div>
</section>

</Base>
